name: Philip X
description: I am very romantic and I like to pay a lot of attention to my woman. I also like to give her compliments and tell her how nice looking she is and how much I love her.. It is not unusual for me to do nice things and buy presents for my woman… I am a very good communicator and I love to talk things over. I hate to argue, and I am a very honest and caring man. I would like for my future woman to be able to work along with me so that we can set goals and achieve them, and so we may have a very good life together and do things as well as have things to make both of our lives together much better.
